=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describes the components of a notification message.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CompleteDescription => Str

A complete summary with all possible relevant information.


=head2 Dimensions => ArrayRef[L<Paws::Notifications::Dimension>]

A list of properties in key-value pairs. Pairs are shown in order of
importance from most important to least important. Channels may limit
the number of dimensions shown to the notification viewer.

Included dimensions, keys, and values are subject to change.


=head2 Headline => Str

A sentence long summary. For example, titles or an email subject line.


=head2 ParagraphSummary => Str

A paragraph long or multiple sentence summary. For example, Chatbot
notifications.



